graph LR
    ODHModelCtrl[odh-model-controller<br/>Operator]

    %% External Dependencies (Required)
    ODHModelCtrl -->|"CRD definitions<br/>InferenceService<br/>ServingRuntime"| KServe[KServe v0.11.0<br/>REQUIRED]
    ODHModelCtrl -->|"Routes API<br/>External ingress"| OSRoutes[OpenShift Routes API<br/>v3.9.0+<br/>REQUIRED]

    %% External Dependencies (Optional)
    ODHModelCtrl -.->|"VirtualService<br/>PeerAuthentication<br/>Traffic mgmt"| Istio[Istio v1.17.4<br/>OPTIONAL]
    ODHModelCtrl -.->|"Autoscaling<br/>KServe Serverless"| Knative[Knative Serving v0.39.3<br/>OPTIONAL<br/>Required for KServe mode]
    ODHModelCtrl -.->|"ServiceMeshMemberRoll<br/>Service mesh integration"| Maistra[OpenShift Service Mesh<br/>Maistra v1+<br/>OPTIONAL]
    ODHModelCtrl -.->|"ServiceMonitor<br/>PodMonitor<br/>Metrics scraping"| PromOp[Prometheus Operator<br/>v0.64.1<br/>OPTIONAL]

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies
    ODHModelCtrl -->|"Watches CRDs<br/>InferenceService"| KServeCtrl[KServe Controller<br/>INTERNAL ODH]
    ODHModelCtrl -->|"Watches Secrets<br/>opendatahub.io/managed=true"| Dashboard[ODH Dashboard<br/>INTERNAL ODH]
    ODHModelCtrl -->|"RoleBinding<br/>prometheus-custom SA"| OSMonitoring[OpenShift Monitoring Stack<br/>INTERNAL ODH]

    %% Integration Points
    K8sAPI[Kubernetes API Server] -->|"API server<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.3"| ODHModelCtrl
    ODHModelCtrl -->|"Watch/Create resources"| K8sAPI

    %% Runtime Dependencies (created by controller)
    ODHModelCtrl -->|creates| Routes[OpenShift Routes]
    ODHModelCtrl -->|creates| VirtualServices[Istio VirtualServices]
    ODHModelCtrl -->|creates| PeerAuth[PeerAuthentications]
    ODHModelCtrl -->|creates| Telemetry[Telemetry resources]
    ODHModelCtrl -->|creates| ServiceMon[ServiceMonitors<br/>PodMonitors]
    ODHModelCtrl -->|creates| NetPol[NetworkPolicies]
    ODHModelCtrl -->|creates| StorageConfig[storage-config Secret]
    ODHModelCtrl -->|creates| RoleBindings[RoleBindings]

    Routes -->|enables| ExternalAccess[External HTTPS Access]
    VirtualServices -->|requires| Istio
    ServiceMon -->|requires| PromOp
    StorageConfig -->|used by| ISVCPods[InferenceService Pods]

    %% External services (runtime)
    ISVCPods -->|"Model artifacts<br/>HTTPS/443<br/>AWS Signature v4"| S3[S3 / Object Storage]

    %% Styling
    style ODHModelCtrl fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:4px,color:#fff
    style KServe fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style OSRoutes fill:#cc0000,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff
    style Istio fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,stroke-dasharray: 5 5
    style Knative fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,stroke-dasharray: 5 5
    style Maistra fill:#cc0000,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff,stroke-dasharray: 5 5
    style PromOp fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,stroke-dasharray: 5 5
    style KServeCtrl fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Dashboard fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style OSMonitoring fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style K8sAPI fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style S3 fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style ISVCPods fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff
